{"hablante":"B","texto":"I get up at six o'clock."},
{"hablante":"A","texto":"Do you have breakfast at home?"},
{"hablante":"B","texto":"Yes, I have breakfast at half past six."},
{"hablante":"A","texto":"What time do you go to work?"},
{"hablante":"B","texto":"I go to work at seven."},
{"hablante":"A","texto":"And what time do you go to bed?"},
{"hablante":"B","texto":"I go to bed at eleven o'clock."}
