{ "titulo": "La rutina de Ana",
"lineas": [
{"hablante":"A","texto":"Do you study in the morning or in the afternoon?"},
{"hablante":"B","texto":"I study in the afternoon. In the morning, I make the bed."},
{"hablante":"A","texto":"What time do you have lunch?"},
{"hablante":"B","texto":"I have lunch at noon."},
{"hablante":"A","texto":"Do you rest after lunch?"},
{"hablante":"B","texto":"Yes, I take a nap. Then I do my homework."},
{"hablante":"A","texto":"What time do you go to bed?"},
{"hablante":"B","texto":"I go to bed at ten o'clock. I always sleep eight hours."}
],
